txt.en: Hlithseld is located in the north of Misthallow.\n\nYou should bring the relics to Hlithseld.
Framsburg can be found in Misthallow.\n\nYou should collect relics within Framsburg.
Within the ruined halls of Framsburg lie many forgotten relics of the Éothéod.
'Good work! I thank you, my friend!'
Within the ruined halls of Framsburg lie many forgotten relics of the Éothéod. You should collect any relics that you find for Léothred. He will surely want to study them further.
